Supports both 2D and 3D development with a unified interface.
GDScript is designed to be user-friendly and Python-like, with fast iteration cycles.
Strong cross-platform support (Windows, Linux, macOS, Android, iOS, and more).
Built-in scene and animation tools for easy creation of complex behaviors.
Fully open-source, with an active community and fast-growing ecosystem.
Supports Visual Scripting for non-coders and C# for more advanced needs.

Website: https://godotengine.org
